No complex setup or documentation needed

Bloxlink appeals to the average user and the advanced user. Setup Bloxlink how you want to, enable new features with the click of a button, seamlessly.

Simple Verification

With the ability to verify through our Roblox game or by a code on your profile, our verification system is very easy to use for new users!

Binds

Connect almost anything on Roblox to a Discord role! Gamepasses, badges, group ranks, and any other asset, it can be done with Bloxlink.

Roblox-based Server Restrictions

Only want group members in your server? We've got you covered. Lock your server with age-limits and group-only with Roblox restrictions.

Group Utility Commands

Bloxlink provides a variety of group features that all types of groups can use to customize their server to their specific style.

User Utility Commands

Ever wanted to know who that John Doe is that joined your server? Use Bloxlink to find out their username and other information!

Community

Tutorials
